Inorder to install these codes, download the PBL_public directory.
Install TNT and JAMA from http://math.nist.gov/tnt/download.html.

In the directory PBL_public :
"cd src/pbl"

In the pbl directory there is a Makefile.
Replace "TNT_PATH = /Users/sanghamitradeb/TNT"
with TNT_PATH= path to directory containing TNT files.

Replace "JAMA_PATH = /Users/sanghamitradeb/JAMA"
with JAMA_PATH= path to directory containing JAMA files.

